      "id": "PopularPost117271",
      "post_content": "The oracle text changes the original functionality of the card in important ways. Removing creatures from combat is something that happens often enough in the game, such as regeneration, or changing controllers during the combat step, that leaving that wording on the card would better represent the original intent of the card. Also, adding the word target changes other interactions unnecessarily.   \n  \nThis text would better represent the original function of the card:  \n  \n2,(T): Choose an attacking creature you control. Untap it and remove it from combat.",
      "posted_by": "zaphod",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost117271\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">The oracle text changes the original functionality of the card in important ways. Removing creatures from combat is something that happens often enough in the game, such as regeneration, or changing controllers during the combat step, that leaving that wording on the card would better represent the original intent of the card. Also, adding the word target changes other interactions unnecessarily. <br/><br/>This text would better represent the original function of the card:<br/><br/>2,(T): Choose an attacking creature you control. Untap it and remove it from combat.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '117271'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy14313\">zaphod</span>\r\n                                (11/21/2010 8:52:58 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.